-neighbours">Good Neighbors</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hana-vu">Hana Vu</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/molly-payton">Molly Payton</a> 、Emily Jeffri、Sienna Spiro 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jacob-alon">Jacob Alon</a> 。</p><p>他们加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-points-east-2024-mitksi-announced-as-final-headliner-buy-tickets-3615254">之前宣布的特别嘉宾 Beabadoobee、TV Girl、Ethel Cain、Arlo Parks、Sir Chloe、Wasia Project、Infinity Song、Wisp、Towa Bird、Strawberry Guy 和 bby 的行列</a>。米茨基的精彩表演将标志着她在为期 10 天的伦敦音乐节上的首次亮相。</p><p>节日日期定于 8 月 18 日星期日在伦敦维多利亚公园举行。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/all-points-east-tickets/artist/5245909?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=RNAxOYVh5xyPWWl31GWJ3xHTUkH3XD09nRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3760218" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3760218" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3760218" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="All Points East 2024 Mitski 海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/All-Points-East-2024-Mitski-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3760218" class="wp-caption-text"> All Points East 2024 Mitski 海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>今年夏天维多利亚公园最受瞩目的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loyle-carner-confirmed-as-first-headliner-for-londons-all-points-east-2024-3542580">Loyle Carner</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/support-line-up-the-postal-service-death-cab-for-cutie-all-points-east-2024-3579830">The Postal Service、Death Cab For Cutie</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaytranada-announced-to-headline-all-points-east-2024-buy-tickets-3593462">Kaytranada</a> 。阵容中的其他艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thundercat">Thundercat</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nas">Nas</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jai-paul">Jai Paul</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixies">Pixies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoenix">Phoenix</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleater-kinney">Sleater-Kinney</a> 。</p><p>米茨基于去年九月发行了她的第七张也是最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mitski-the-land-is-inhospitable-and-so-are-we-review-3496153">“The Land Is Inhospitable And So Are We”</a> 。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对该系列的四星评论中写道：“《荒凉之地……》中的选择和安排是米茨基最复杂、最丰富的作品之一，但它们却转化为如此简单，一种声明，其中有痛苦和痛苦。”爱，仅此而已。这些是我们制造一切的原料。”</p><p>这位艺术家在伦敦的最后一次演出是去年 10 月在联合教堂举行的，这场演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/mitski-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3513100">获得了<em>NME</em>的五星级好评</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，沃特豪斯此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suki-waterhouse-shares-two-new-singles-ahead-of-coachella-performance-3616837">在科切拉音乐节演出之前发行了两首全新单曲“My Fun”和“Faded”</a> 。</p><p> 4月11日，这位歌手、演员兼模特在社交媒体上分享说，她已经发行了《My Fun》和《Faded》，并确认这两首歌将成为她“下一张专辑”的一部分。目前尚不清楚有关该专辑的更多细节。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suki-waterhouse-and-men-i-trust-lead-new-special-guests-for-mitski-at-all-points-east-2024-3760216">Suki Waterhouse 和 Men I Trust 在 2024 年 All Points East 上为 Mitski 领衔的新特邀嘉宾</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》的奥利·赛克斯 (Oli Sykes) 解释了比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 合作传闻是如何产生的https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizo​​ns-oli-sykes-explains-how-billie-eilish-collab-rumours-came-about-3760211?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=奥利赛克斯给我带来地平线解释比莉艾利什合作谣言是如何产生的Emma WilkesTue, 28 May 2024 20:15:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3760211 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利·赛克斯和比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我知道 Billie 和我们一起创作歌曲的机会微乎其微”</p><p> 《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》的奥利·赛克斯 (Oli Sykes) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首先发表了一篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizons-oli-sykes-explains-how-billie-eilish-collab-rumours-came-about-3760211">，解释了比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 的合作谣言是如何产生的</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥利·赛克斯和比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/oli-sykes-billie-eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>主唱奥利·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oli-sykes">赛克斯 (Oli Sykes)</a>解释了乐队将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>合作的传闻是如何产生的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》——《后人类：下一代》评论：夸张而精彩</a></strong></li></ul><p>有传言称，早在一月份，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oli-sykes">赛克斯</a>在艾利什的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C12gJjlvKug/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram 帖子</a>上发表了一条写着“豪华轿车”的评论后，两人就开始合作，粉丝们认为这是他们当时未发行的专辑 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">《Post Human: Nex》</a>中的曲目之一 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">将军</a>。</p><p>然而，当这张专辑在周五（5 月 24 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-bring-me-the-horizons-new-album-post-human-nex-gen-3759124">提前一天发布</a>时，Eilish 根本没有出现在唱片中，而《liMOusIne》中的客座嘉宾来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">AURORA。</a></p><p>现在，赛克斯在<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m001zbdp" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">接受《Radio 1 Rock Show》丹尼尔·P·卡特采访时解释了谣言的来源。</a>事实证明，赛克斯向艾利什发送了这首歌的未完成版本，但从未得知她是否能够听到。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bring Me The Horizo​​n - liMOusIine（歌词视频）ft. AURORA" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/e8U96n8L-lg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “比莉的事情就是这样：她的摄影师是她的忠实粉丝，他们提到了她创作一首歌的想法，”赛克斯说。 “所以我给她发了‘豪华轿车’。距离它完全完成的状态已经过去了很长一段时间。我的意思是，我不能百分百地说她听了，但我知道她听了。</p><p> “所以我认为‘liMOusIne’对除了我之外的任何人都没有任何意义，也许她看到这条评论后，[我]把它留在了她的 Instagram 上，没想到一两周后，当我们巡演时，我们将文件名放在我们的视频中，然后每个人都将其连接起来。”</p><p>他继续说道：“这似乎是一种尝试获得媒体关注的廉价方式，但事实并非如此。当我发现时，我实际上非常尴尬 - 就像，“天哪，不！”因为我知道 Billie 和我们一起创作歌曲的机会微乎其微。”</p><p>然而，粉丝们确实从巡演视觉效果中正确地看出，Bring Me The Horizo​​n <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-looks-like-a-bring-me-the-horizon-and-underoath-collaboration-is-on-the-way-3569048">与</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underoath">Underoath</a>合作了歌曲“a balleT w/my name On”。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对该专辑的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">四星评论</a>中写道：“很少有现代摇滚乐队能制作出一张如此对声音和色彩进行轰炸的专辑。乔丹·菲什之后，他们仍然保持着原来的样子：一种超越个人个性的创造力。这完全证明了四年的等待是合理的，这已经像是古老的历史了。系好安全带——因为这<i>仍然</i>是 BMTH 的世界，我们还将在其中生活相当长的一段时间。”</p><p> 《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》的奥利·赛克斯 (Oli Sykes) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上首先发表了一篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizons-oli-sykes-explains-how-billie-eilish-collab-rumours-came-about-3760211">，解释了比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 的合作谣言是如何产生的</a>。</p> ;
